    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.poster.avif?t=1758547825\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.webm?t=1758547825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.mp4?t=1758547825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>ABOUT STORY</strong><br>Having completed her education at the monastery, Princess Asteria returns to her country and finds that her Virtuous Kingdom has been destroyed.<br>The sorcerer of the Saban Kingdom named Dragos invades the kingdom with his army. <br>The Sorceress invades the Virtous Kingdom and traps Astreia on her own continent.<br>Asteria embarks on an adventure to get her revenge and her kingdom back. Mearth II is the sequel to the first game.<br>An adventure awaits you, be prepared for difficult challenges and roads.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/32fa982da62baa641ff4309755e4051a.poster.avif?t=1758547825\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/32fa982da62baa641ff4309755e4051a.webm?t=1758547825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/32fa982da62baa641ff4309755e4051a.mp4?t=1758547825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Spells and magical weapons </strong>: Use your magical powers and weapons to beat enemies and bosses, as well as pass levels <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Stealth executions </strong>: You can sneak behind some enemies and kill them  also kill enemies with finishing execution hits in some fights </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Fight your way </strong>: Define your own playstyle, and prepare for the challenges that await in your own unique way </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Brutal enemies and bosses </strong>: You will not get bored while fighting bosses with different characteristics. While battling ruthless enemies, you can dodge their attacks with your skill </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Majestic structures and dangerous roads </strong>: Get ready for spectacular and atmospheric maps that will keep you in the game, but beware of the traps on the roads you walk </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/fc782d2af38adc7b77c9fc62bd0ed9f4.poster.avif?t=1758547825\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/fc782d2af38adc7b77c9fc62bd0ed9f4.webm?t=1758547825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197990/extras/fc782d2af38adc7b77c9fc62bd0ed9f4.mp4?t=1758547825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Obstacles and puzzles </strong>: Solve puzzles and dodge obstacles to progress through caves </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Witness a story </strong>: Explore the dark and magical story of the Mearth universe with Asteria. </li></ul></ul></li></ul>",
